<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870128-0156 </DOCNO><HL> Retail Sales Increase in Japan</HL><DD> 01/28/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> JAPAN </IN><DATELINE> TOKYO  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Sales at Japan's major retail stores rose 1.4% in December from a year earlier, the Ministry of International Trade and Industry said. The growth slowed from November's record 6.8% increase. </TEXT></DOC>